"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-showbiz-adam-peaty-olympics-katya-jones-strictly-paris-bbc-show-scandal-b1173419.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Showbiz  Sign up to our free weekly newsletter for exclusive competitions, offers and theatre ticket deals    I would like to be emailed about offers, event and updates from Evening Standard.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 420, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourprivacy notice.\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Katya Joneshas paid tribute to friend and formerStrictly Come DancingpartnerAdam Peatyafter watching him win\\u00a0silver in the 100m breast-stroke final at theOlympicsin Paris.\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 611, \"end\": 616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 6.4057736758623335e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Russian professional dancer, 35, was paired with the swimmer, 29, on the show in 2021 and was in the French capital on Sunday supporting him alongside his mother Caroline, and his girlfriend Holly Ramsay, plus, their three-year-old son George.\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 623, \"end\": 630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9298656930698493, \"rank\": 0.07406442457248641, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 724, \"end\": 730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9346806777443837, \"rank\": 0.0690169682827849, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 785, \"end\": 793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Kennedy\", \"score\": 0.9070233288026313, \"rank\": 0.09970963703472782, \"text\": \"Caroline\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Kennedy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Kennedy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jones shared a number of pictures and videos on social media capturing Peaty's big moment and took to Instagram the day after to reflect on his achievements and pay tribute.\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 1041, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He did it.\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have so much respect for this guy.\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Such a wholesome human, which shows in and out of the pool,\\\" her post began.\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As he said, in his heart he has won.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1207, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And he will always be our champion.\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Well done @melmarshallmassive , we know it will not be possible without you.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1320, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It felt very personal last night to be there and watch him swim.\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And so special to be part of the support gang for Adam!\\\"\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our champ always\\\", Jones declared, alongside a clip she filmed of Peaty receiving his silver medal after coming in\\u00a0joint-second with\\u00a0Nic Fink, with Nicolo Martinenghi taking gold, adding: 'He is such an incredible man.\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1580, \"end\": 1588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nic_Fink\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nic Fink\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nic_Fink\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nic_Fink\"}, {\"begin\": 1595, \"end\": 1613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\", \"score\": 0.9999999871765796, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nicolo Martinenghi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Someone who has gone through so much, yet remained so dignified.\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1730, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They will love you always and regardless of any results.\\\"\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jones and Peaty's staunch display of friendship comes as Strictly faces its biggest crisis in its 20 years, as a wave of complaints from past celebrity contestants have been made in recent months over claims of \\\"abuse\\\" and \\\"bullying\\\".\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 2024, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Professional\\u00a0Graziano Di Prima, 30, was axed from the showfollowing claims he hit and spat at his dancing partner\\u00a0Zara McDermott, 27, during rehearsals for last year's series.\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2140, \"end\": 2154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Love_Island_(2015_TV_series,_series_4)\", \"score\": 0.9999999211609096, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zara McDermott\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Love_Island_(2015_TV_series,_series_4)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Love_Island_(2015_TV_series,_series_4)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Giovanni Pernice, 33, was suspended while the broadcaster launches an investigation into claims of off-camera misconduct made by Sherlock actress\\u00a0Amanda Abbington, 50, and two other former celebrity partners.\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2209, \"end\": 2225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giovanni_Pernice\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Giovanni Pernice\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giovanni_Pernice\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giovanni_Pernice\"}, {\"begin\": 2355, \"end\": 2371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanda_Abbington\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amanda Abbington\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanda_Abbington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanda_Abbington\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Italian native has vowed 'I will be back'and has reportedly provided a dossier of evidence to the BBC probe that he believes will exonerate him.\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2567, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2423, \"end\": 2430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italians\", \"score\": 0.8793081054205772, \"rank\": 0.07515565225342159, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italians